node.text:
The most affected region by Coronavirus in Italy 💔 Lombardia is located in the center of Italy and Europe. Home to a variety of industries such as agriculture, manufacturing, fashion and eco-tourism. ⠀

The breathtaking landscape of Lombardy is a mixture of hills, mountains, lakes and plains. Its Alpine area is very popular in winter by skiers. Nature lovers are greeted by beautiful shoreline along the great Lombard lakes: Lake Garda, Lake Como, Lake Maggiore and Lake Iseo. ⠀

Stay strong Italy! 💚🤍❤️ #ForzaItalia

Video by @idressitalian ⠀

Always #wondermore

Visit: https://wonderlustcollective.co

Devil’s Pool is a natural pool of water that’s situated atop of Victoria Falls, renown for being among the largest waterfalls in the world. Right on the edge of this massive waterfall, a calm pool of water forms. 

This is known as the Devil’s Pool Victoria Falls. And daring visitors can actually swim in this pool straddling the edge of Victoria Falls!

node.text:
⠀
"Summer Show" 🌕🪐

A week ago, the two biggest planets Jupiter and Saturn had an appointment with the full blue moon (the 2nd full moon of the same month) for an unprecedented spectacle. I wanted to mark the occasion with this composition. Sizes and distances are not to scale, and have been intentionally accentuated for a more artistic effect. 

📸 by @astronophilos 

#wondermore
